snippet.title: Just Stuff from Scarlett Johansson, Kevin Costner, Spawn, Amber Heard to My Birthday!!
snippet.description:
Source:
https://www.spreaker.com/user/nerdintexas/just-stuff-from-scarlett-johansson-kevin

In this episode, i talk about Scarlett Johansson and Disney have beef. Kevin Costner returns to Iowa, Spawn gets a new writer, Amber heard posts on Instagram about prepping for Aquaman 2. Ryan Reynolds in Fortnite. Emma Stone returns for Cruella 2. Venom gets delayed and a bunch of movies coming out in September. I talk about my birthday and what I got to do!!! 
Roundrockdonuts.com
If you want to buy me tacos for my birthday head on over to
buymeacoffee.com/nerdintexas
